Ontological Engineering 
©Asunción Gómez-Pérez,
Ontology Reengineering [33] refers to the process of 
retrieving and transforming a conceptual model of an existing 
and implemented ontology into a new, more correct and more 
complete conceptual model which is reimplemented.
